OL,3,CD-Day anniversary: Commemoration
OL,4,Cevents begin in Normandy
OL,6,FVeterans who lost friends on the very
OL,7,Fsame beaches made the journey to
OL,8,FFrance and will be attending the
OL,9,Fannual Ceremony of Remembrance at the
OL,10,FBritish Normandy Memorial.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FKey figures in the success of the
OL,18,Flandings are being honoured, including
OL,19,FField Marshal Montgomery.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
