OL,3,CD-Day anniversary: Commemoration
OL,4,Cevents begin in Normandy
OL,6,FLater, his grandson Henry Montgomery
OL,7,Fis set to complete the final day of
OL,8,Fhis journey "In Monty's Footsteps" by
OL,9,Fwalking more than 22km across Sword,
OL,10,FJuno and Gold beaches ` at the very
OL,11,Ftime the first troops landed.
OL,13,FEach step of his two-month journey
OL,14,Facross Britain and north-western
OL,15,FFrance honoured the lives of more than
OL,16,F22,000 men and women whose names are
OL,17,Fengraved on the British Normandy
OL,18,FMemorial.
