OL,3,CD-Day anniversary: Commemoration
OL,4,Cevents begin in Normandy
OL,6,FHe is joined by Will Ramsay, grandson
OL,7,Fof Admiral Ramsay, Commander-in-Chief
OL,8,Fof the Naval Forces on D-Day.
OL,10,FThis year, the smallest number of
OL,11,FNormandy veterans will attend the
OL,12,Fceremony since the memorial opened in
OL,13,F2021, with only six confirmed.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
